CSR, Zoran Report Merger to Combine Imaging, Wireless Products

-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-02-21T02:46:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/csr-zoran-report-merger-to-combine-imaging-wireless-products.html
  CSR Plc , a London-based wireless-
technology producer, will merge with  Zoran Corp . of the U.S.,
which specializes in imaging technology, the companies announced
today.  Following the merger, worth $679 million, Zoran
shareholders will own approximately 35 percent of the enlarged
CSR, the companies said in an e-mailed statement.  The new company will produce multimedia devices such as
Internet-enabled cameras, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Jordan in  London  at 
 jjordan22@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 